y":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T08:21:11.000Z","msg":"Construction人打骰，有撚創科？<br />\n除左Civil/BSE，其他engine都係吉祥物嚟"},{"pid":"c11cdb2f29e381ef1797e3a0a4b60e597a4e0fa7","tid":2174049,"uid":333026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T15:14:25.000Z","msg":"又係建造業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a200f62bd432b87e235fa4123a627605bb7fa413","tid":2174049,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:48:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}